<span id="freeTextContainer17257895011859575428">I was not expecting “Yellow Crocus” by Laila Ibrahim to be such a fantastic read. This book has been on my shelf for a few years now. Just shows how quickly we can pass by a jewel. I am now started reading “Mustard Seed” by Laila Ibrahim which is a sequel to “Yellow Crocus”. </span>

