              <span id="reviewTextContainer1093361308" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9224432278558224182"><br/>This is the wonderful, heart-wrenching, but also heart-warming story of the relationship between a young white girl and her slave nanny.<br/><br/>Beautifully written and simply told. I finished it in one sitting.</span>

          </span>
